    ...    into Power On state using RTE OC buffers. Implementation
    ...    must be compatible with the theory of operation of a
    ...    specific platform.
    Restore Initial DUT Connection Method
    IF    '${DUT_CONNECTION_METHOD}' == 'SSH'    RETURN
